---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout title="HCI Portfolio | Evaluation">
    <PageHeader 
        title="Evaluation & Refinement" 
        description="Testing our prototypes with users, gathering feedback, and refining the experience."
    />

    <Section title="User Testing Sessions">
        <div class="mb-8 bg-brand-yellow p-6 border-4 border-black shadow-neo inline-block transform rotate-1">
            <p class="text-black text-xl font-bold leading-relaxed">
                We conducted usability testing sessions to validate our design decisions and identify areas for improvement.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Placeholder for testing methodology and setup -->
        <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 mb-8 shadow-neo transform -rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6 font-display uppercase border-b-4 border-black pb-2 inline-block">Testing Methodology</h3>
            <ul class="text-black font-bold text-lg space-y-4 border-l-4 border-brand-accent pl-4">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-accent text-2xl leading-none">→</span> (Number of participants)</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-accent text-2xl leading-none">→</span> (Testing format: e.g., remote, moderated)</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-brand-accent text-2xl leading-none">→</span> (Key tasks tested)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </Section>

    <Section title="Key Findings & Refinements" class="bg-brand-orange border-y-4 border-black relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="mb-12 bg-white p-6 border-4 border-black shadow-neo inline-block transform -rotate-1">
                <p class="text-black text-xl font-bold leading-relaxed">
                    Based on the feedback gathered, we iteratively improved the prototype. Here are the major changes we made.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-16">
                <!-- Refinement Item 1 -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-neo-lg transform rotate-1">
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-black text-2xl uppercase mb-2 border-b-4 border-black pb-1 inline-block">Issue Identified</h4>
                        <p class="text-black font-bold text-lg mb-6 bg-brand-pink border-2 border-black p-2 inline-block shadow-neo">(Describe what users struggled with)</p>
                        
                        <h4 class="font-black text-2xl uppercase mb-2 border-b-4 border-black pb-1 inline-block">Our Solution</h4>
                        <p class="text-black font-bold text-lg bg-brand-green border-2 border-black p-2 inline-block shadow-neo">(Describe how the design was changed to fix it)</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-cyan border-4 border-black flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-neo">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-10"></div>
                        <span class="font-mono font-bold text-black text-xl bg-white px-4 py-2 border-4 border-black">BEFORE_AFTER.img</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Refinement Item 2 Placeholder -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-neo-lg transform -rotate-1">
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-black text-2xl uppercase mb-2 border-b-4 border-black pb-1 inline-block">Issue Identified</h4>
                        <p class="text-black font-bold text-lg mb-6 bg-brand-yellow border-2 border-black p-2 inline-block shadow-neo">(Describe what users struggled with)</p>
                        
                        <h4 class="font-black text-2xl uppercase mb-2 border-b-4 border-black pb-1 inline-block">Our Solution</h4>
                        <p class="text-black font-bold text-lg bg-brand-green border-2 border-black p-2 inline-block shadow-neo">(Describe how the design was changed to fix it)</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-pink border-4 border-black flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-neo">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-10"></div>
                        <span class="font-mono font-bold text-black text-xl bg-white px-4 py-2 border-4 border-black">BEFORE_AFTER.img</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Section>
</Layout>